    "rationale": "Overall credibility assessment accepted despite Test Conditions factor achieving level 2 against required level 3. All three QoIs satisfy quantitative acceptance criteria (E/uval < 1.96, percent difference < 10%). Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 factors meet or exceed required levels. The single-condition limitation is documented and accepted given the regulatory context of ASTM F1717 as a standardized test method.",
